{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "希里丝（铳士Ver.） 第5话 打破隔阂的撞击！",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "哈～视察之旅也快结束了。\\n见识了不少城市，\\n真是一趟愉快的旅行！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊，不过我可是被你拖着\\n耍得够呛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "唔！谁、谁让……\\n每个城市的文化都那么有趣呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "希里丝你看起来，\\n是真的很开心呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "我也是……能够认识\\n北大陆城市的各种人……\\n我很开心。谢谢，你们！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诺艾尔……我们才要道谢！\\n接下来的旅途也拜托你带路啦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "好、好的。那么，那个……\\n我们还是赶紧，\\n通过这一带，比较好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "为啥啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "这里，拉施特伦附近的\\n小国之间，有很多小纷争。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "会有当过佣兵的人\\n和亡国的余党兵袭击路人……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "是吗……也就是说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "嗯……现在跟在我们\\n身后的家伙就是那种人了吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "啧……被发现了啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那还用说！可不要小瞧\\n森隐族的听力啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "哼，不过就凭你们三个……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "看这训练有素的动作……\\n是余党兵的，那一伙！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "这、这群人是余党兵！？\\n为什么会袭击我们啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "哈，想必你们不会懂\\n失去国家苟且偷生的滋味！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "即便如此，我们也有必须\\n要保护的家人和同胞……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "就算抛弃自尊\\n沦为盗贼也无所谓……\\n抱歉，你们就在此长眠吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "咦？\\n没、事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "希里丝阁下，你没事吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "你、你是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "龙……我认识他！\\n他还来过圣城几次，\\n记得是叫……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "是的，我乃隶属于普劳达空军\\n镇压部队的AC-011 加兰德。\\n请多指教，卢卡阁下。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "加、加兰德！\\n谢谢你！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "普劳达？啧……是那群喜欢\\n干预人类战争的好事之龙。\\n你是来消灭我们的吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "并不是。我只是发现争执，\\n当机立断保护了希里丝阁下……\\n并非特意冲你们而来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "我奉普劳达本部之命\\n前来和诸位谈话。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "什么？普劳达，要和我们谈话？\\n你们有什么企图？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "普劳达并无企图。\\n只是想将拉施特伦\\n从长久的争斗中解放出来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "解放？什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "毁灭诸位故乡的国家\\n如今正在各地横行霸道，\\n逐步扩张版图。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "在其威胁到整个北大陆的和平之前，\\n希望能和亡国的残存势力合作，\\n一同打倒该国，故特来相助。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "那个……就是说加兰德\\n你要加入这些人，\\n帮他们打仗的意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "是、是的。我觉得是这个意思。\\n普劳达是根据自己的判断\\n为阻止战争而活动的武装龙集团。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "为了给拉施特伦带来和平，\\n我猜他们，是决定了\\n要干预这地区的战争……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "和平……那不是个好机会吗？\\n只要赢了这场战争，你们没准\\n就又能夺回自己的祖国了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "我拒绝……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶！为什么啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "拉施特伦自古就是为龙所喜爱，\\n受其恩泽的地方……\\n我们一直对龙心怀敬爱。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "但是，你们普劳达是例外。\\n因为你们打破了我们一直\\n信仰的龙所遵守的规矩。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "龙的规矩？那是指……\\n过去的……龙不能直接\\n干预人类纷争这一点吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "是的……北大陆是伊莉雅教的\\n发源地，相比南大陆，\\n严格遵守规矩的人更多……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "对于这些人来说，\\n打破规矩的普劳达\\n无异于舍弃了信仰……所以……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "正是……这群家伙失去了\\n祖先们遵守、传承下来的东西，\\n已经不算是龙了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "只是野兽而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "什么！我说！\\n你说的也太过分了吧！？\\n加兰德他们也是有理由……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "希里丝阁下，请等一下。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "加兰德！？为什么要阻止我？\\n他们在说你的坏话啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "就算你帮我出头，恐怕也无法\\n让他们改变主意。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "自古传承下来的文化\\n无法突然改变。\\n谁都没有这种权力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "话是这么说，但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "哼，你既然明白，又何必来这里。\\n反正你们不过是一群\\n只会以武力服人的家伙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "啊～真是的……\\n不行！我忍无可忍了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "唔啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "众人",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "你这女人，干什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "给我纠正！\\n纠正你对加兰德说的话！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "让我纠正？\\n你生活在与普劳达结盟的国家，\\n让我纠正也……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "和普劳达还有国家\\n什么的没关系！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我……见过很多\\n珍惜不同文化的人们。\\n也互相交流，一起哭一起笑过！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "以什么为重，如何选择，\\n这些会根据种族出身各有不同。\\n这的确是每个人的自由，但是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "根本不打算理解对方就恶言相向，\\n无论在什么情况下……\\n都绝对是错的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "希里丝阁下……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "对、对啊……\\n确实，什么都不知道\\n就全盘拒绝并不好。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "（紧张）……\\n那、那个，各位！\\n请听我说！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "加兰德打破规矩的原因……\\n和权力还有信仰都无关，\\n是为理想做出的重大决断。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "你说这群家伙有理想？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "是、是的……加兰德他们\\n普劳达的龙对北大陆\\n旷日持久的战争倍感忧心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "虽然也有人说他们只是\\n想用武力支配别人……\\n但他们只是想亲手保卫故乡。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "想保卫……北大陆这个故乡？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "诺艾尔阁下……\\n我很欣慰你能表示理解。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "以及……拉施特伦的诸位，\\n我不求你们理解，只是……\\n这片大地的惨状已不忍直视。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "从前，这里有美丽的雷纳河，\\n还有针叶树繁茂的赤色森林。\\n但如今……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "赤色森林已经……在灭国的那天\\n化为灰烬了。雷纳河如今\\n也成了流淌着鲜血之河……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "……\\n原来你们也和我们一样，\\n凝视着相同的景象……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "我知道了……\\n你是叫加兰德吧？\\n我纠正刚才说你是野兽的话。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01",
                "110340_01",
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "众人",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "真、真的吗！？谢谢你！\\n诶嘿嘿，原来大叔你是个好人呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "余党兵",
            "context": "哼，少套近乎。\\n我并没有说要协助你们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嗯嗯，这样也可以啊！\\n首先要彼此了解，\\n这是非常美好的事哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "要先从了解彼此的文化开始！\\n不做出理解他人的努力……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "就无法跨出第一步！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "呼……南大陆好暖和啊。\\n北方的空气虽然也不错，\\n但还是这里让人踏实。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "希里丝阁下。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "加兰德！北大陆一别好久没见，\\n拉施特伦那边已经没问题了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "是的，那之后我和余党兵交涉，\\n顺利建立起了合作关系。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "真的？太好了！\\n他们愿意好好听你说话了啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "多亏了希里丝阁下。\\n不然我可能也会因为\\n根深蒂固的老规矩就轻易放弃了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "你、你太夸张啦。\\n我只是撞了他一下而已……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "AC-011 加兰德",
            "context": "不，你那一撞相当精彩。\\n到底是进行了什么样的训练\\n才能做到那样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "啊哈哈……这个嘛，那个……\\n只是看着我那笨蛋哥哥，\\n身体就会不由自主地动起来而已……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "希里丝你真厉害啊。\\n和加兰德都能打成一片。听说你\\n在视察之旅中也大显身手来着……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唉……我可是被她\\n耍得够呛。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不过，和她一起旅行让我意识到，\\n像她那样直率地冲入其中，\\n反而容易打破文化的隔阂。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "以她那天真无邪的心灵……\\n也许能和全世界的人打成一片呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊哈哈，是啊。希里丝也许\\n能开创一个了不起的未来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210117_01",
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那种未来是你我都无法做到……\\n只有她能开创的，\\n天真无邪又充满温暖的世界。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
